</li>
</ol>
<p>Ultimately, the decision depends on your technical skills, budget, timeframe, and specific needs. If you're experienced with electronics and programming, and have the time and resources, creating your own camera could be a rewarding project. However, if you prefer a quicker and potentially more cost-effective solution, exploring available products designed for streaming footage might be the right choice.</p></div>

