    line-height: 1.6;">If i want to search for repeat periode of earthquake, the paper i read has a b value for earthquakes with magnitutes of 5. Do i have to recalculate the b value if wanna get the periode for earthquakes with m=7?</div><br/><br/>LLM response:<br/><div style="
